7. 包安装:
链接: https://dominoc925.blogspot.com/2019/09/installing-vim-youcompleteme-for-ubuntu.html

sudo apt install vim-youcompleteme
vim-addon-manager install youcompleteme

卸载:
sudo apt remove vim-youcompleteme

